<!-- Display -->
<div class="sg-h2">Display</div>
<div class="sg-note">To make an element render block, inline or inline-block i.e. change it's <code class="sg-code">display</code> value, apply the: <code class="sg-code">class="block"</code>, <code class="sg-code">class="inline"</code> or <code class="sg-code">class="inline-block"</code> helper classes to the element.</div>

<p><span class="inline">I'm rendering inline</span>, <span class="inline-block">I'm rendering inline-block</span> <span class="block">I'm rendering block.</span></p>
<!-- //Display -->

<!-- Vertical Alignments -->
<div class="sg-h2">Vertical Alignments</div>
<div class="sg-note">To change the vertical alignment of any element that is <code class="sg-code">display: inline;</code> or <code class="sg-code">display: inline-block;</code> apply the: <code class="sg-code">class="align-top"</code>, <code class="sg-code">class="align-middle"</code>, <code class="sg-code">class="align-baseline"</code> or <code class="sg-code">class="align-bottom"</code> helper classes to the element.</div>

