<!-- Text-->
<div class="sg-h2">Text</div>
<div class="sg-note">Various helper classes specifically for text.</div>

<div class="sg-h3">Size</div>
<div class="sg-note">To increase or decrease the text size from the base text size apply the: <code class="sg-code">class="txt-sml"</code>, <code class="sg-code">class="txt-lrg"</code> or <code class="sg-code">class="txt-reset"</code> helper classes. This helper class is not suitable for headings.</div>
<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, <ins class="txt-sml">I'm small text</ins> consectetuer adipiscing elit. <ins class="txt-lrg">I'm large text</ins> ligula eget dolor. <ins class="txt-reset">I'm default text size</ins>.</p>

<div class="sg-h3">Alignments</div>
<div class="sg-note">To change the horizontal alignment of some text apply the: <code class="sg-code">class="txt-center"</code>, <code class="sg-code">class="txt-left"</code> or <code class="sg-code">class="txt-right"</code> helper classes.</div>
<p class="txt-center">I'm center aligned, lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. ligula eget dolor.</p>
<p class="txt-left">I'm left aligned, lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. ligula eget dolor.</p>
<p class="txt-right">I'm right aligned, lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. ligula eget dolor.</p>

<div class="sg-h3">Styles</div>
<div class="sg-note">To apply different font style treatments of some text apply the: <code class="sg-code">class="txt-italic"</code>, <code class="sg-code">class="txt-bold"</code> or <code class="sg-code">class="txt-caps"</code> helper classes.</div>
<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, <span class="txt-italic">I'm italicised text</span> consectetuer adipiscing elit. <span class="txt-bold">I'm bolded text</span> ligula eget dolor. <span class="txt-caps">I'm all caps</span>.</p>


<div class="sg-h3">Truncate</div>
<div class="sg-note">To truncate some text apply the: <code class="sg-code">class="txt-truncate"</code> helper class to the element.</div>
